		<h1 style="font-size: 2em;">Democracy Now! Needs You</h1>
		<h2 style="padding-left: 0.5em;"><a href="/donate/120810S">We need your help today.</a></h2>
        <p>From WikiLeaks' releases of the Iraq War Logs and diplomatic cables to the climate change talks in Cancun, Bolivia and Copenhagen; from the epicenter of the earthquake in Haiti to health insurance executive-turned-whistleblower Wendell Potter exposing how the insurance companies wanted to "push Michael Moore off a cliff"; you come to Democracy Now! for news you can trust.</p>  

		<p><a href="/donate/120810S">If you turn to Democracy Now! to deepen your understanding of what is happening in the world, please make your tax-deductible contribution today.</a></p>

		<p>When you want the news about the wars in Iraq and Afghanistan, you need media not brought to you by military contractors or sponsored by weapons manufacturers.</p>
          
        <p>When Democracy Now! brings you news about the ongoing health care crisis, you can be sure that our coverage is not being paid for by the insurance corporations or by Big Pharma.</p>  

        <p>Democracy Now! is <strong>your</strong> daily grassroots global news hour.</p>
          
        <p><a href="/donate/120810S">We can only do this with your help. Your donation to Democracy Now! today is an investment in true investigative journalism.</a></p>

        <p>Your support sustains our work.  Thank you for making Democracy Now! what it is today, and what it can be tomorrow.</p>

        <p><a href="/donate/120810S">Donate $80 or more today, and we'll send you a signed copy of Amy Goodman's newest book, Breaking the Sound Barrier or other great gifts!</a></p>
        <div id="pop_footer">
            <button id="pop_donate_button">Donate Now!</button> <button id="pop_cancel_button">No Thanks!</button><br/>
